events.name: Alabama Crimson Tide at Ohio State Buckeyes

headlines.description: Cardale Jones came through again at the Sugar Bowl in his second career start and Ezekiel Elliott ran for 230 yards, leading Ohio State to a 42-35 upset of top-ranked Alabama in the College Football Playoff semifinal Thursday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ohio St. stuns Bama in Sugar

events.name: Oregon Ducks at Florida State Seminoles

notes.headline: Rose Bowl Game Presented by Northwestern Mutual - CFB Semifinal

headlines.description: Marcus Mariota and Oregon turned an avalanche of Florida State mistakes into a mountain of points, and the Ducks rolled past the defending national champions 59-20 on Thursday to turn the first College Football Playoff semifinal into a rout.
headlines.shortLinkText: Ducks down FSU in Rose Bowl rout

events.name: Michigan State Spartans at Baylor Bears

headlines.description: No. 7 MSU shocks No. 4 Baylor 42-41 in Cotton Bowl
headlines.shortLinkText: MSU stuns Baylor with flourish in 4th

events.name: Missouri Tigers at Minnesota Golden Gophers

headlines.description: Marcus Murphy ran for 159 yards, Russell Hansbrough added 114 yards and a touchdown and No. 16 Missouri beat Minnesota (No. 25 CFP) 33-17 on Thursday in the Buffalo Wild Wings Citrus Bowl.
headlines.shortLinkText: Mizzou tops Gophers in Citrus Bowl

headlines.description: Melvin Gordon rushed for an Outback Bowl-record 251 and three touchdowns and Rafael Gaglianone kicked a 25-yard field goal in overtime to give No. 18 Wisconsin a 34-31 victory over No. 19 Auburn on Thursday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Gordon, Badgers top Auburn in OT
